mfw. mfw, or MFW, stands for Mikey Fuckin' Way, which is a nickname for Mikey Way, the bassist for New Jersey alternative band My Chemical Romance. Term became widely known when a black t-shirt featuring 'MIKEY FUCKIN' WAY' was worn by him and was being sold on the MCR merch website
